				<baseName xml:lang="zh">硫酸铜</baseName>
			</name>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">basic copper sulfate; BSC copper fungicide; CP basic sulfate; tri-basic copper sulfate; blue vitriol; Roman vitriol; bluestone</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">basic copper sulfate; BSC copper fungicide; CP basic sulfate; tri-basic copper sulfate; blue vitriol; Roman vitriol; bluestone</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification name="ILCD 1.1" classes="../ILCDClassification.xml">
					<common:class level="0">Materials production</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Inorganic chemicals</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Copper sulfate is an inorganic compound that combines copper and sulfate. It occurs in various forms such as anhydride, a monohydrate, and the pentahydrate, which is used as a fungicide or algicide. The pentahydrate forms a blue, crystalline, odorless solid with a metallic taste. It occurs in nature as the mineral chalcanthite. Copper sulphate is the salt of sulphuric acid and copper, formed at the second degree of oxidation. It is a crystalline, odourless powder that excellently absorbs water.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硫酸铜是一种由铜和硫酸盐组成的无机化合物。它有多种形态，如酸酐、一水合物和五水合物，五水合物可用作杀真菌剂或杀藻剂。五水合物是一种蓝色结晶状无味固体，带有金属味。它在自然界中以矿物黄铜矿的形式存在。硫酸铜是硫酸和铜在二度氧化时形成的盐。它是一种结晶状无味粉末，吸水性极强。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>CuSO4</sumFormula>
